                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Descenders",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Primordial One is one of the entities from another world, whose wills can rival an entire world.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Shades",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Primordial One created four shining shades and reshaped Teyvat along with them.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dragon Sovereigns",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Before the appearance of the Primordial One, the world was ruled by elemental dragons. After a forty-year war, the dragons were defeated and the seven nations submitted to the First Throne. The Primordial One stole the dragon's authority and later used it for the divine thrones.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Second Who Came",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Second Throne, invaders from another world who destroyed the barrier around Teyvat created by the First Throne and brought people hope for freedom. The war with the Second Descenders brought forbidden knowledge, many plagues, and destruction to Teyvat.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "One Who Came After",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Severely wounded in the great war of vengeance, the Primordial One had their functions ruined and could no longer use their absolute authority to suppress the original order of this world. To continue to subdue and control the resentments and loathing of the world, the First Throne and one who came after created the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4935,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/15/94376896/d233949972be14fcf0feb738a9b67efa_4817492893140404510.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
